the Chaldeans; eastern Aramaic, or the Aramaic used in
Chaldea.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Chaldee Paraphrase</b></col>, <cd>A targum written in
